org.cef.handler

类 CefPrintHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.callback.CefNativeAdapter
      • org.cef.handler.CefPrintHandlerAdapter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    CefNative, CefPrintHandler 

    public abstract class CefPrintHandlerAdapter
extends CefNativeAdapter
implements CefPrintHandler
    An abstract adapter class for receiving print events on Linux. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects.
    用于在Linux上接收打印事件的抽象适配器类。此类中的方法为空。此类存在是为了创建处理程序对象的便利。

      • getPdfPaperSize

        public java.awt.Dimension getPdfPaperSize(int deviceUnitsPerInch)
        从接口复制的说明: CefPrintHandler
        Called when PrintToPDF is requested for a browser. Returns the page size (as measured in microns) to use.
        在为浏览器请求PrintToPDF时调用。返回要使用的页面大小（以微米为单位）。
        指定者:
        getPdfPaperSize 在接口中  CefPrintHandler
        参数:
        deviceUnitsPerInch - The DPI of the print. Use this to calculate the page size to use. - 印刷品的DPI。使用此选项计算要使用的页面大小。
        返回:
        The page size 页面大小

        从接口复制的说明: CefPrintHandler

      • onPrintSettings

        public void onPrintSettings(CefPrintSettings settings,
                            boolean get_defaults)
        从接口复制的说明: CefPrintHandler
        Synchronize |settings| with client state. If |get_defaults| is true then populate |settings| with the default print settings. Do not keep a reference to |settings| outside of this callback.
        同步|设置|与客户国家。如果| get_defaults |是的，然后填充|设置|使用默认打印设置。不要保留对| settings |的引用在这个回调之外。
        指定者:
        onPrintSettings 在接口中  CefPrintHandler

      • onPrintStart

        public void onPrintStart(CefBrowser browser)
        从接口复制的说明: CefPrintHandler
        Called when printing has started for the specified |browser|. This method will be called before the other onPrint*() methods and irrespective of how printing was initiated (e.g. CefBrowser::print(), JavaScript window.print() or PDF extension print button).
        在指定的浏览器|开始打印时调用。此方法将在其他onPrint *（）方法之前调用，而不管如何启动打印（例如CefBrowser :: print（），JavaScript window.print（）或PDF扩展打印按钮）。
        指定者:
        onPrintStart 在接口中  CefPrintHandler
